data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!! Welcome to the LAKE LIFE! This exquisite property offers a comfortable and spacious three-bedroom, two-bath home located right on Adams Lake! This home features high ceilings, an open floor plan that allows natural light to come in throughout, tile flooring, a custom bar, home security system, and surround sound; to name a few. The home features an abundance of storage options, including spacious walk-in closets. The primary draws in spectacular views! The primary bath has a walk-in shower and showcases a separate jetted tub that's perfect for relaxing after a long day. The landscaping is equipped with a sprinkler system, along with a 30 amp RV hook up, two storage sheds and a large detached carport- perfect to store all your fishing and water toys. Walk outside onto your dock and sit under the gazebo - enjoying picturesque views of the sunset over the water! This home has many features that are perfect for entertaining with family and friends! Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own and enjoy the serenity and tranquility this lake home lifestyle has to offer. Call to schedule your tour!
